    <item>
      <title>宝马看到关税，中国低迷对卡门制造利润的重量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/bmw-sees-tariffs-china-slump-weighing-on-carmaking-profit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宝马AG的碳化利润将远远低于今年的长期目标，这是由于美国和欧洲之间的贸易紧张局势加剧而降低了中国的销售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/bmw-sees-tariffs-china-slump-weighing-on-carmaking-profit</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 06:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希腊评级升级提供了债务危机关闭的途径</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/greek-rating-upgrade-offers-path-to-debt-crisis-closure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[希腊可以通过信用升级将其摆脱其债务危机的最后遗迹，从而将其从15年前进入的垃圾领土上最终撤出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/greek-rating-upgrade-offers-path-to-debt-crisis-closure</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国告诉越南在关税风险中提高贸易余额</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/vietnam-s-trade-minister-meets-us-trade-chief-amid-tariff-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国贸易代表杰米森·格里尔（Jamieson Greer）告诉越南最高贸易官员，他的国家必须改善两国之间的贸易平衡，并进一步开放其市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/vietnam-s-trade-minister-meets-us-trade-chief-amid-tariff-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 01:17:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
